        <updateDate>2019-07-26T22:23:38Z</updateDate>
        <text><![CDATA[ <p><b>Jake Laird Act of 2018</b></p> <p>This bill authorizes the Department of Justice to make grants to states to implement laws that authorize a law enforcement officer to seize firearms from a person if there is probable cause to believe the person is dangerous.</p>]]></text>
      </summary>
